{"tid":928791,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[挑機/轉載]Epic Games 宣布推出 Epic Games Store 平台","createTime":"2018-12-05T06:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T07:43:26.000Z","uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"efb40f0c5b4368db1c23688f034694e8ae27557f","tid":928791,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>挑戰 Steam 等遊戲發行平台！Epic Games 宣布推出 Epic Games Store 平台</strong><br />\n<br />\nEpic Games 創辦人 Tim Sweeney 今日宣布，Epic Games 將推出 Epic Games Store 平台（Epic Games 商城），將與遊戲研發者共同為玩家帶來眾多 PC 與 Mac 遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/97/648b1c637803faee5eeb590f7f1369d5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F97%2F648b1c637803faee5eeb590f7f1369d5.JPG&h=ca4a7ad0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nEpic Games 在推出《要塞英雄：大逃殺》後獲得相當大的迴響，使他們擁有一定的市場規模經濟，但《要塞英雄》的 PC Android 版並沒有透過一般玩家熟悉的 GOOGLE PLAY 平台上架，而是在自家平台推出，當初就引發遊戲界熱烈討論。<br />\n <br />\n如今 Epic Games 宣布將推出 Epic Games Store 平台，不僅將營運自身遊戲，同時也將成為遊戲開發者另一個發行管道選擇，等於向其他遊戲發行平台如 Steam 等下戰帖。Tim Sweeney 表示，Epic Games 商城上架的遊戲，開發者將可以獲得利潤中的 88%，且不受任何等級或門檻限制，若是遊戲是採用 Epic Games 旗下 Unreal 引擎來製作，那 12% 中的 Epic Games 利潤將可以抵研發者 5% 的引擎分成費用。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/98/3ba0b05001298fb05629dd0d611369e5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F98%2F3ba0b05001298fb05629dd0d611369e5.JPG&h=25698dcf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">圖片來源：Epic Games</div></span><br />\nTim Sweeney 表示，開發者可以自行掌控商城中自己遊戲的頁面，而 Epic Games Store 將歡迎使用任何遊戲引擎研發的遊戲。至於未來在 Epic Games Store 上架的遊戲內容，預定將於美國時間 12 月 6 日 The Game Awards 舉行之後公開。<br />\n<br />\n轉載自巴哈姆特：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/9/172059.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F9%2F172059.html&d=mtzj3xCnlAAwmkpThMn1EYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=25a8af69\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/9/172059.html</a>"},{"pid":"04d1d9b98cf929dae1dea0f4ca6dee2b5c5f40ec","tid":928791,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"88%比返developor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔知佢地個平台會唔會逼你綁定平台定可以雙修"},{"pid":"da9f58b5b5971b3559a84cd397bcc309d1e8d838","tid":928791,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"steam 分你30%真係食水深 唔怪得近年咁多發行商都搞自己個平台"},{"pid":"c869798b7b1cfc32d40e9fb38eaf8a21d466526e","tid":928791,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da9f58b5b5971b3559a84cd397bcc309d1e8d838","tid":928791,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"steam 分你30%真係食水深 唔怪得近年咁多發行商都搞自己個平台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"都唔係新鮮事，最慘係有部份indie用UE4做仲要比多5% epic games<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f01274a1e045c7939d719211f8aeddd164ce3c9","tid":928791,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:11:14.000Z","msg":"無人討論下?"},{"pid":"b4d988d0221752d9929a86b3c355343a5c3cca28","tid":928791,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}